# Google Ad Manager — rewarded ad unit path for web.
# Get this from your Google Ad Manager account after creating a
# "Rewarded" ad unit. Leave unset for local dev: the app falls back
# to a 5-second demo countdown instead of a real ad.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your real ad unit path.
VITE_GAM_REWARDED_AD_UNIT=/1234567/tarot_rewarded
